question: Tī sńg-bái ê gîn-tô-phiò ê goā-úi-seng chè-chok hō͘-chhin ê chu-liāu tiong, nńg-lâng ê chè-chok hō͘-chhin sī siáⁿ-mih lūi ê chè-chok hō͘-chhin ê phòe-chùn cheng-kim ê chòe-tōa ki-lān ê sńg-bái ê gîn-tô-phiò ê kî-kan?
Ūi-hô tio̍h-sī chāi 'sìn-iōng kip' ū tiāⁿ-chòe, chi̍t-pâi 'bōe phài-hō' sī ū '2014' ê chióng-lūi hō-chòe pó-chèng ê chóng kim-ê thian-tiâu? (gîn-bī bān-giâm)
Tī si in-sò͘ ū siōng koâi ê choân-thé chham-siâⁿ chiàⁿ-lâm, siáⁿ chi̍t khoán phiah-chè-lūi ('investment grade', 'non-investment grade', 'bô phiah-chè') chòe siâⁿ chē ê pō͘-hun ê choân-thé?
answer: maximum potential amount of future payments investment grade

question: Tī tsuan-tîng ê siu-chi̍t-hō siōng tāi ê chîⁿ-lō͘ hō͘-chhut lāi-bīn, ū sîn-me phiah-phóe sī sǹg 'bōe hō͘-phêⁿ'?
Nāi-koán `sek-li̍t hō͘-tō͘ tōa thè-chè` ê `bô phòe-chhú` ê chi̍t ê chîⁿ-sò͘ nāi-koán hiān-chāi ê sû-tiāⁿ chhiau-kòe 10%, tō ē-tàng chū-chi̍t koh chhut nn̄g-ê sán-phín ê tōa chē-chi̍t ê chha-tó͘?

In 'total' si-a^ siong chē ê choa^ phoe ê chîm-pài ê iâⁿ-kè, hō͘ siáⁿ-chóng lūi ê piau-chún tē-ūi chiap-chhiap ê hō͘-tō͘ (investment grade) kap hui chiap-chhiùⁿ tē-ūi (non-investment grade) lóng sī 0 í-ki̍p chō-chha̍h-chú ('2014') ê chu-liāu?
Koh-iáⁿ ê hō͘-chîⁿ phòe-chè (chòe-hó tit-ê, bô-tit-ê, í-ki̍p bô phòe-chè) lóng ū siâⁿ-chē 2014 ê chu-liāu?
answer: maximum potential amount of future payments investment grade
maximum potential amount of future payments non-investment grade

question: Tùi chitê khòan su-liāu lâi kóng, siáⁿ chi̍t ê “siāng tōa ê chē-siâⁿ bu̍t” tī “siū-khoân-téng ê siū-tóe-kim chòe-tōa khó-lêng-hêng ê chîⁿ” chit ê bô͘ ê lāi-bīn? Benz ū siáⁿ iân-khóan iân-khóan?
answer: “Sîn-hū-sìn lâi siū-tóe-kim” chit ê lūi-hêng, bô͘-téng ū $94.2 îⁿ, sī siāng tōa ê chē-siâⁿ bu̍t. Chit ê sò͘-jī pí tòe ê siāng tōa ê lūi-hêng (“iáⁿ-chè siong-phín hō͘-chòe pó-chèng” ū $67.9 îⁿ) koân chiâⁿ chē 38.4%, iân-khóan ū bô͘-téng ê 7 ê lūi-hêng ê tiong-kan-tiâu (7 ê lūi-hêng ê tiong-kan-tiâu sī $38.11 îⁿ) koân chiâⁿ chē 2.4 pèi. Tùi tòe chi̍t hong-bīn, “pó-chèng siū-tóe hō͘-chòe siong-phín” kap “hō͘-chòe ê tōa-tōa ê chi̍t-ê siong-phín” sī siāng chē-siâⁿ ê chiáⁿ-hong chē-siâⁿ bu̍t, bô͘-téng chi̍t-ê chi̍t-ê sī $0.3 îⁿ.

question: Kha-koaⁿ 'performance guarantees' kah 'custody indemnifications and other' ê chha-put lêng-khoah ê tōa-khòaiⁿ hō͘ sann-ê teng-kip thiah-khòaiⁿ, che tùi che lióng chióng pó-chèng ê ui-hiam thiau-kiāⁿ ū sím-mih ê su-siâⁿ?
answer: Ūi 'performance guarantees', in ê iáⁿ-chú tī chha-liâng téng-kip ($5.7B), hui-chha-liâng téng-kip ($5.0B), kah bô chha-liâng ($5.6B) tiong hun-pò͘ chin tōa-khòaiⁿ, chí-sī in ê ui-hiam tûng-sai hun-pò͘ chin chē. Kòe-àn, 'custody indemnifications and other' chin tōa-khòaiⁿ tī chha-liâng téng-kip ($18.5B), hui-chha-liâng téng-kip chió-chió ($3.1B), chi̍t-ê bô chha-liâng ê iáⁿ-chú bô. Che piáu-sī 'custody indemnifications' kap 'performance guarantees' pí-kàu khah séng-tâi ê téng-kip ui-hiam tûng-sai pí-kàu khah séng-tâi ê khòaiⁿ.

question: Tâi-oân ê 'investment grade' kap 'non-investment grade' ê chî-thâu chòe chē ê sî-chūn chhoan-thok kim-ê liáu-kái, ū bô koh ū chi̍t-ê bûn-tè ê koan-liân, chū-iû kok-chióng ê hō͘-chhiâⁿ lūi-hêng? Kái-soeh lí ê lí-iû.
answer: Bô, bô chi̍t-ê bûn-tè ê koan-liân. Kan-na ū saⁿ-ê lūi-hêng ū sò͘-jī ê nn̄g chi̍t-ê cūi-chiáⁿ, chu-liāu bái thài-kóa pó͘-kè lâi kiàn-li̍p ū sìn-tō ê phó͘-lōe. 'Financial standby letters of credit' ū chi̍t-ê chin koân ê investment grade cūi-chiáⁿ ($49.2B) kap chi̍t-ê chin koân ê non-investment grade cūi-chiáⁿ ($28.6B). 'Performance guarantees' ū kāng-khoán ê cūi-chiáⁿ chiáⁿ ($5.7B kap $5.0B). Put-koh, 'custody indemnifications' ū chi̍t-ê koân ê investment grade cūi-chiáⁿ ($18.5B) tān-sī chi̍t-ê chin-kē ê non-investment grade cūi-chiáⁿ ($3.1B), che tò-péng kî-thaⁿ nn̄g ê tiám só͘ thê-chhut ê chi̍t-ê ti̍t-chiap ê chiâⁿ-koan koan-liân. Kúi-ā-ê só͘-chāi ê táu-chí-á cūi-chiáⁿ hō͘ lán bô-hoat-tō͘ chìn-chi̍t lâi hoat-tō͘ chho-cha.

question: Chiah ū siōng-toā ê investment grade tùi bī-lâi hêng-chhit ê hū-kuan tîng-tōo?
